1. `var a = new A();`的过程可以理解为：

    ```javascript
    function A() { this.lastname = "Terry"; }
    A.prototype.sayHello = function () { console.log('hello'); };
    var a = { firstname: 'Frank' };
    A.call(a);
    a.__proto__ = A.prototype; // don't use private properties like this
    // console.log(a) => Object { firstname: "Frank", lastname: "Terry" }
    ```
2. null

    ```javascript
    var a = null; // null object,  typof a === "object"
    var b = {};   // empty object, typof b === "object"
    ```
<!--more-->

3. prototype chain

    ```javascript
    var Person = function () { this.lastname = 'Terry'; };
    Person.prototype.family = (new Date()).getTime();
    Person.prototype.sayHello = function () { console.log('hello'); };

    var Employee = function (firstname) { this.firstname= firstname; };
    var p = new Person();
    Employee.prototype = p;

    // everything from the prototype is inherited, including constructor
    // if restore it mannually, the DontEnum flag won't be set, and it will appear in for..in loop
    //   so do not use it???
    // Employee.prototype.constructor = Employee;

    Employee.prototype.fullName = function () { console.log(this.family, this.firstname, this.lastname); };

    var john = new Employee('John');

    var frank = new Employee('Frank');
    frank.lastname = 'Lampard';
    /////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    john.__proto__           === Employee.prototype === p // john instanceof Employee
    john.__proto__.__proto__ === Person.prototype         // john instanceof Person

    john.__proto__.fullName                    john.__proto__.lastname    john.__proto__.family
     ↑                                          ↑                          ↑
    john.fullName()          john.firstname    john.lastname              john.family

    frank.__proto__.fullName                                              frank.__proto__.family
     ↑                                                                     ↑
    frank.fullName()         frank.firstname   frank.lastname             frank.family
    ```

4. 自定义函数：重写自身的函数体，使第二次及后续的调用做更少的工作

    ```javascript
    var scareMe = function () {
      alert("Boo!");
      scareMe = function () {
        alert("Double boo!"); // 执行第一次以后，scareMe会被“重新定义”
      };
    };
    scareMe.property = "properly";

    var prank = scareMe; // assigning to a different name
    var spooky = { boo: scareMe }; // using as a method

    prank(); // "Boo!"
    prank(); // "Boo!"
    console.log(prank.property); // "properly"

    spooky.boo(); // "Boo!"
    spooky.boo(); // "Boo!"
    console.log(spooky.boo.property);   // "properly"

    // 以上引用都指向了“旧”函数，以下已被替换为“新”函数
    scareMe(); // Double boo!
    scareMe(); // Double boo!
    console.log(scareMe.property); // undefined
    ```

5. 类式继承的Holy Grail

   ```javascript
   var inherit = (function () {
     var F = function () {};
     return function (C, P) {
       F.prototype = P.prototype;
       C.prototype = new F();
       C.uber = P.prototype;
       C.prototype.constructor = C;
     }
   }());
   ```
